00:02:39.390 --> 00:02:40.810
How did I get involved
with this?

00:02:40.810 --> 00:02:42.740
Well I'm an architect
as a profession.

00:02:42.740 --> 00:02:44.600
And I went to school with
Nicholas Negroponte

00:02:44.600 --> 00:02:46.120
at MIT in the 1960s.

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:48.020
So we are both architects.

00:02:48.020 --> 00:02:51.060
And I went back into practice
in the private world.

00:02:51.060 --> 00:02:56.570
But 30 years ago I met with him
and we started the first

00:02:56.570 --> 00:03:02.240
